                      "value": "A contingency table built with skimage.evaluate.contingency_table. If None, it will be computed with skimage.evaluate.contingency_table. If given, the entropies will be computed from this table and any images will be ignored."
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
